                      10. CHALLENGES AND SOLUTIONS
================================================================================

Challenge 1: Concurrent Booking
Problem: Multiple users booking same seats simultaneously
Solution: Implemented database transactions with row-level locking to prevent 
         double booking

Challenge 2: Waitlist Management
Problem: Automatic confirmation when seats become available
Solution: Created background queue manager to monitor cancellations and 
         trigger auto-confirmation

Challenge 3: Complex Fare Calculation
Problem: Dynamic pricing based on multiple factors
Solution: Developed modular fare calculation system considering distance, 
         class, quota, and surge pricing

Challenge 4: Seat Allocation Algorithm
Problem: Optimal seat assignment with berth preferences
Solution: Implemented intelligent allocation algorithm grouping families and 
         respecting preferences

Challenge 5: Performance Optimization
Problem: Slow search for trains with multiple routes
Solution: Database indexing, query optimization, and caching of frequently 
         accessed data

Challenge 6: Security Concerns
Problem: Protecting user data and preventing unauthorized access
Solution: Implemented industry-standard security practices including password 
         hashing, CSRF protection, and input validation

